          "overrides": {
            "label": "Document Requirements",
            "content": "A copy of the birth certificate should be uploaded by all Non-Nationals. Caricom Nationals also have to upload a certificate of Immigration Status for the Parent. All other Non-Nationals should upload a copy of Immigration Status for the child. Persons unable to upload these documents should submit physical copies to the school.",
